	</t3>
	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div align="center">
			<div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color:#DFF0D8;border-color:#D6E9C6;color: #468847;padding: 1px 0;">
				
				<h3><a href="//www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-cityguide">Joomla template for Travel and Tour Guides - JA City Guide</a></h3>
				
				<h4><a href="//www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-cityguide" title="">Home</a> | <a href="//joomlart.com/demo/#ja_cityguide" title="">Demo</a> | <a href="http://www.joomlart.com/documentation/joomla-templates/ja-cityguide" title="">Document</a> | <a href="//pm.joomlart.com/browse/JATCCITYGU" title="">Changelog</a></h4>

				<p>JA City Guide is dedicated travel and tour guide Joomla template with creative and modern design and advanced features for travel, tour guide and directory web sites. JA City Guide supports JA Mega Filter Joomla extension and JomSocial component to build social pages.</p>

				<span style="color:#FF0000">Note: T3 blank requires T3 plugin to be installed and enabled.</span><p></p>
				<p>Copyright 2004 - 2019 <a href='http://www.joomlart.com/' title='Visit Joomlart.com!'>JoomlArt.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<style>table.adminform{width: 100%;}</style>
		</div>
		]]>
	</description>
